# Each default sensor registers exactly once on Start.
each_default_sensor_registers_once|create_collector
each_default_sensor_registers_once|add_default_sensor|total_cpu
each_default_sensor_registers_once|add_default_sensor|process_memory
each_default_sensor_registers_once|add_default_sensor|collector_alive
each_default_sensor_registers_once|start
each_default_sensor_registers_once|stop
each_default_sensor_registers_once|expect_registration_count|3
